text: Bendigo is a city in Victoria, Australia. Bendigo may also refer to: ==Places== * City of Greater Bendigo, a local government area in Victoria, Australia * Division of Bendigo, Australian electoral division in Victoria, Australia * Bendigo, New Zealand, a settlement and historic area ==Other uses== * Bendigo (horse), a thoroughbred racehorse * HMAS Bendigo, two ships of the Royal Australian Navy * William Thompson (boxer) (1811–1880), English bare-knuckle boxer ==See also== * Greater Bendigo National Park, in Victoria, Australia * Bendigo Box-Ironbark Region, a tract of land in Victoria, Australia
title: Bendigo (disambiguation)
